\id OBA - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h Obadia 
\toc1 Obadia 
\toc2 Obadia 
\toc3 Oba 
\mt1 Obadia 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Fweny mag Obadia. 
\b  
\b  
\p Magi e weche ma Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto wacho kuom Edom. 
\q1 Wasewinjo wach; koa kuom Jehova Nyasaye. 
\q2 Jaote oseor ir ogendini mondo owach niya, 
\q1 “Chunguru, wadhi waked kode.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 “To neuru, abiro miyo udok matin e kind ogendini, 
\q2 bende ibiro chau ahinya. 
\q1  
\v 3 Sunga manie chunyu osewuondou, 
\q2 un mudak e kind lwendni, 
\q2 kendo ugero miechu kuonde motingʼore, 
\q1 un ma uwacho kendu niya, 
\q2 ‘En ngʼa manyalo dwokowa piny?’ 
\q1  
\v 4 To kata obedo ni unyalo fuyo malo mabor ka ongo, 
\q2 kendo ugero kar daku maber e kind sulwe malo, 
\q1 to koa kuno abiro dwokou piny,” 
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho. 
\q1  
\v 5 “Ka jokwoge obironu, 
\q2 jomecho mag otieno, 
\q1 to mano kaka masira malich ritou, 
\q2 donge gibiro kwalo mwandu magu kaka ginyalo? 
\q1 Ka jopon mzabibu obiro iru 
\q2 donge digiwe olemb mzabibu matin? 
\q1  
\v 6 To mano kaka Esau ibiro choko gigene 
\q2 kendo mwandune mopandi noyaki! 
\q1  
\v 7 Ogendini ma uriworugo biro sembou nyaka giko mar tongʼ; 
\q2 osiepeu biro wuondou ma lowu; 
\q1 kendo joma chamo chiembu biro ketonu obadho, 
\q2 to ok unufweny.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, 
\q2 “Odiechiengʼno donge abiro tieko jorieko mag Edom, 
\q2 jogo man-gi winjo e gode mag Esau? 
\q1  
\v 9 Jolweny magi, yaye Teman, 
\q2 biro bedo kod bwok kendo ji duto modak, 
\q2 e gode mag Esau ibiro negi. 
\q1  
\v 10 Nikech lweny mane utimone owadu Jakobo 
\q2 unubed gi wichkuot; 
\q2 mi nokethu nyaka chiengʼ. 
\q1  
\v 11 Chiengʼ mane ichungʼ tenge 
\q2 ka joma moko donjo e dhorangeyene, 
\q1 kendo gigoyo ombulu 
\q2 ne Jerusalem, 
\q2 ne ichal mana kodgi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ne ok onego ungʼigi kod achaya 
\q2 chiengʼ masichgi, 
\q1 bende ne ok onego ubed mamor 
\q2 chiengʼ mane ikethoe Juda, 
\q1 kata bedo gi ngʼayi 
\q2 chiengʼ chandruokgi. 
\q1  
\v 13 Ne ok onego udonj e dhorangeye mag joga 
\q2 chiengʼ mane masira omakogi, 
\q1 kata ngʼiyogi gachaya e thagruokgi, 
\q2 kata kawo mwandugi, 
\q1 e chiengʼ thagruokgi 
\q2 gi chiengʼ masichegi. 
\q1  
\v 14 Ne ok onego uchungʼ e akek yore, 
\q2 ka ugengʼone jogegi maringo, 
\q1 kendo ne ok onego uchiw jogegi motony e lwet wasikgi 
\q2 chiengʼ chandruokgi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 “Chiengʼ Jehova Nyasaye okayo machiegni 
\q2 ne ogendini duto, 
\q1 bende kaka isetimo e kaka notimni, 
\q2 timbeni nodwogi e wiyi iwuon. 
\q1  
\v 16 Mana kaka ne umer ewi goda maler 
\q2 e kaka ogendini duto, biro metho ametha, 
\q1 ginimeth ametha 
\q2 ma ginichal joma onge. 
\q1  
\v 17 To ewi got mar Sayun tony nobedie, 
\q2 mi enobed kama ler, 
\q1 kendo od Jakobo 
\q2 nokaw girkeni mage. 
\q1  
\v 18 Od Jakobo nobed mach 
\q2 kendo od Josef mach nokaknie, 
\q1 od Esau nobed chuk mach, 
\q2 mi ginimoke moliel pep, 
\q1 onge ngʼat ma notony 
\q2 koa e od Esau.” 
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye osewacho. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Jo-Negev nokaw 
\q2 piny gode mag Esau, 
\q1 kendo joma odak e tiend gode 
\q2 nokaw piny jo-Filistia, 
\q1 ginikaw nyaka piny Efraim gi Samaria, 
\q2 eka jo-Benjamin nokaw piny Gilead. 
\q1  
\v 20 To oganda mar jo-Israel mane oter e twech e piny Kanaan, 
\q2 nokaw pinyno nyaka chop Zarefath, 
\q1 kendo jo-Jerusalem manie twech, 
\q2 e piny Sefarad biro kawo miech Negev. 
\q1  
\v 21 Jores noidhi ewi got mar Sayun, 
\q2 mi ginibed kod loch ewi gode mag Esau, 
\q2 kendo pinyruoth duto nobed e lwet Jehova Nyasaye.